## Objective
Build a component to list all sprints for an instance in a structured view (e.g. accordion or timeline).

## Requirements
- Create a `client/src/components/SprintList.tsx` component.
- The component should accept an array of sprint objects as props.
- Each sprint should display its ID, title, and goal.
- Sprints should probably be collapsible (accordion style) to hide/show their inner tracks and tasks.
- If a sprint has no tracks or tasks yet, display an appropriate empty state.
